HOW TO, release a new gui version:
*********************************

- copy CL_code/code into LFMM_GUI_toCompile

- update the commands in the lfmm_gui.cpp file:
tr("code\\LFMM.exe -n %1 -L %2 -K %3 -i %4 -b %5 -g \"%7\" 
-v \"%8\" -o \"%9\" -p %10 -C \"%11\" -D %12 -d %13 -m")

- follow the READMEÂ to create a new executable for each OS,
	WIN, linux32, linux64, MacOS.

- for windows, compile the CL-code to add it in the directory.

- for mac, create an installer (if necessary)

- create a different release for each OS, based on the previous
version of the release. Each one is different.
